{
  "title": "第1周 第2天 — 合同总体结构",
  "objective": "掌握英文商务合同的总体结构框架，识别并理解合同各组成部分的英文名称及其功能，为后续逐层深入学习奠定基础。",
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "grammar",
      "heading": "1. 核心词汇",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "英文商务合同的结构高度标准化。无论是股权收购协议、服务合同还是保密协议，其骨架基本一致。以下 12 个术语构成了合同结构的核心词汇。"
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "headers": [
            "英文",
            "音标",
            "中文",
            "常见搭配"
          ],
          "firstColWord": false,
          "rows": [
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"合同标题\">title</span>",
              "/ˈtaɪtl/",
              "n. 合同标题；所有权",
              "contract <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"合同标题\">title</span>; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"合同标题\">title</span> of the agreement; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"合同标题\">title</span> page"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"前言/序言\">preamble</span>",
              "/priːˈæmbəl/",
              "n. 序文；前言",
              "the <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"前言\">preamble</span> of this Agreement; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"前言\">preamble</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">clause</span>; as <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定/载明\">set forth</span> in the <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"前言\">preamble</span>"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span>",
              "/rɪˈsaɪtəlz/",
              "n. 鉴于条款；背景叙述",
              "the <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议附；附于本协议\">hereto</span>; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span> section; as described in the <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span>"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"定义条款\">definitions</span>",
              "/ˌdefɪˈnɪʃənz/",
              "n. 定义条款",
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"定义条款\">definitions</span> and interpretation; as <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"已定义的\">defined</span> in <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span> 1; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"已定义的\">defined</span> terms"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"实质条款\">operative provisions</span>",
              "/ˈɒpərətɪv prəˈvɪʒənz/",
              "n. 实质性条款；正文条款",
              "the <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"实质条款\">operative provisions</span> of this Agreement; key <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"实质条款\">operative provisions</span>"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款/通用条款\">boilerplate</span>",
              "/ˈbɔɪlərpleɪt/",
              "n. 通用条款；标准条款",
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款\">boilerplate</span> clauses; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款\">boilerplate</span> provisions; standard <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款\">boilerplate</span> language"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表/附件\">schedules</span>",
              "/ˈʃedjuːlz/",
              "n. 附件；附表",
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表\">schedules</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附于本协议的\">attached hereto</span>; as set out in Schedule A; schedule of <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"交付成果\">deliverables</span>"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">clause</span>",
              "/klɔːz/",
              "n. 条款",
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"终止\">termination</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">clause</span>; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"违约金条款；惩罚性条款\">penalty clause</span>; pursuant to <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">Clause</span> 5.2"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定/条款\">provision</span>",
              "/prəˈvɪʒən/",
              "n. 规定；条款",
              "general provisions; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"以…为条件/受…约束\">subject to</span> the provisions of; key provisions"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">article</span>",
              "/ˈɑːrtɪkəl/",
              "n. 条；章",
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span> 3 of this Agreement; under this <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span>; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">article</span> by <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">article</span>"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案/修改\">amendment</span>",
              "/əˈmendmənt/",
              "n. 修正案；修订",
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span> to the Agreement; first <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span>; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span> and restatement"
            ],
            [
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署/执行\">execution</span>",
              "/ˌeksɪˈkjuːʃən/",
              "n. 签署；执行",
              "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span> of this Agreement; <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span> copy; upon <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span>"
            ]
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "html": "<strong>辨析：<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">clause</span> vs. <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定\">provision</span> vs. <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">article</span></strong><br>三者均可译为“条款”，但使用场景有别。<strong><span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span></strong> 通常指合同的大章节编号（如 <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span> 1, <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span> 2），层级最高。<strong><span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">Clause</span></strong> 指具体的条文，偏口语化，也常用于指某一特定条款（如 <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"终止\">termination</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">clause</span>）。<strong><span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定\">Provision</span></strong> 最为通用，既可指单条条款，也可泛指一组条款（如 general provisions），语域最正式。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "examples",
      "heading": "2. 例句与语境",
      "groups": [
        {
          "heading": "2.1 合同标题与序言",
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "This Share Purchase Agreement (“Agreement”) is entered into <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"自…起\">as of</span> January 15, 2026.",
              "translation": "本《股权收购协议》（以下简称“本协议”）于2026年1月15日签订。"
            },
            {
              "text": "The <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"前言\">preamble</span> identifies the parties to this Agreement and the date of <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span>.",
              "translation": "序文载明本协议的当事人及签署日期。"
            },
            {
              "text": "The <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定\">set forth</span> the background and purpose of the transaction contemplated <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议中\">herein</span>.",
              "translation": "鉴于条款阐述了本协议所述交易的背景和目的。"
            },
            {
              "text": "Unless otherwise <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"已定义的\">defined</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议中\">herein</span>, capitalized terms used in this Agreement <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> have the meanings ascribed to them in <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span> 1 (<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"定义条款\">Definitions</span>).",
              "translation": "除本协议另有定义外，本协议中使用的大写术语应具有第一条（定义）中赋予的含义。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "2.2 合同正文与结构",
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "The <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"实质条款\">operative provisions</span> of this Agreement <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> become effective upon <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span> by both parties.",
              "translation": "本协议的实质性条款自双方签署后生效。"
            },
            {
              "text": "Each <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">article</span> of this Agreement addresses a distinct aspect of the parties' rights and <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"义务（复数）\">obligations</span>.",
              "translation": "本协议各条分别针对当事人权利义务的不同方面。"
            },
            {
              "text": "The Seller's <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"义务（复数）\">obligations</span> under <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">Clause</span> 4.2 are <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"以…为条件\">subject to</span> the <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条件（复数）\">conditions</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定\">set forth</span> in <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span> 6.",
              "translation": "卖方在第4.2条项下的义务须受第六条所列条件的约束。"
            },
            {
              "text": "Any <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span> to this Agreement <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> be in writing and duly executed by all parties <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议附；附于本协议\">hereto</span>.",
              "translation": "对本协议的任何修订均须以书面形式作出，并经全体当事人正式签署。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "2.3 通用条款与附件",
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "The <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款\">boilerplate</span> provisions, including severability and entire agreement clauses, are contained in <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span> 12.",
              "translation": "通用条款，包括可分割性条款和完整协议条款，载于第十二条。"
            },
            {
              "text": "The <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表\">schedules</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附于本协议的\">attached hereto</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> form an integral part of this Agreement.",
              "translation": "本协议所附附件构成本协议不可分割的组成部分。"
            },
            {
              "text": "The provisions of this Agreement <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> survive the <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span> and delivery of the closing documents.",
              "translation": "本协议之条款在交割文件签署交付后继续有效。"
            },
            {
              "text": "This Agreement has been executed in two counterparts, each of which <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> be deemed an original.",
              "translation": "本协议一式两份签署，每份均视为正本。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence-analysis",
      "heading": "3. 长难句拆解",
      "items": [
        {
          "title": "长难句 1",
          "sentence": "Unless otherwise <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"已定义的\">defined</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议中\">herein</span>, capitalized terms used in this Agreement <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> have the meanings ascribed to them in <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span> 1 (<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"定义条款\">Definitions</span>), and any reference to a “<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">Clause</span>” or “<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span>” <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> be construed as a reference to a <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">clause</span> or <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">article</span> of this Agreement.",
          "structure": [
            "<strong>条件状语：</strong>Unless otherwise <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"已定义的\">defined</span> <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议中\">herein</span> — 除非本协议另有定义",
            "<strong>主句1：</strong>capitalized terms ... <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> have the meanings ascribed to them in <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span> 1 — 大写术语具有第一条中的含义",
            "<strong>并列主句2：</strong>any reference to a “<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">Clause</span>” or “<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">Article</span>” <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> be construed as ... — 对“条款”或“条”的提及应解释为……",
            "<strong>关键搭配：</strong><span class=\"collocation\">ascribed to</span>（赋予）；<span class=\"collocation\">construed as</span>（解释为）"
          ],
          "translation": "除本协议另有定义外，本协议中使用的大写术语应具有第一条（定义）中赋予其的含义，且对“条款”或“条”的任何引用均应被解释为对本协议中相应条款或条的引用。"
        },
        {
          "title": "长难句 2",
          "sentence": "The <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表\">Schedules</span> and Exhibits <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附于本协议的\">attached hereto</span> and referred to <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议中\">herein</span> are <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"兹；特此\">hereby</span> incorporated in and made a part of this Agreement with the same force and effect as if <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定\">set forth</span> in full in the body <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议的\">hereof</span>.",
          "structure": [
            "<strong>主语：</strong>The <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表\">Schedules</span> and Exhibits — 附件和附录",
            "<strong>后置定语1：</strong><span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附于本协议的\">attached hereto</span> — 附于本协议的",
            "<strong>后置定语2：</strong>and referred to <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议中\">herein</span> — 并在本协议中提及的",
            "<strong>谓语：</strong>are <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"兹；特此\">hereby</span> incorporated in and made a part of this Agreement — 特此纳入本协议并成为其组成部分",
            "<strong>状语：</strong>with the same force and effect as if <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定/载明\">set forth</span> in full in the body <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议的\">hereof</span> — 具有与在本协议正文中全文载入同等的效力",
            "<strong>关键搭配：</strong><span class=\"collocation\">attached hereto</span>（附于本协议）；<span class=\"collocation\">incorporated in</span>（纳入）；<span class=\"collocation\">with the same force and effect</span>（具有同等效力）"
          ],
          "translation": "附于本协议并在本协议中提及的各附件和附录，特此纳入本协议并构成其组成部分，与在本协议正文中全文载入具有同等效力。"
        },
        {
          "title": "长难句 3",
          "sentence": "No <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span>, modification, or <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"弃权\">waiver</span> of any <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定\">provision</span> of this Agreement <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> be effective unless it is in writing and signed by the <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"当事人\">party</span> against whom enforcement of such <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span>, modification, or <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"弃权\">waiver</span> is sought.",
          "structure": [
            "<strong>主语：</strong>No <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span>, modification, or <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"弃权\">waiver</span> of any <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定\">provision</span> of this Agreement — 对本协议任何条款的修订、修改或弃权",
            "<strong>谓语：</strong><span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> be effective — 不具有效力",
            "<strong>条件状语：</strong>unless it is in writing and signed by the <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"当事人\">party</span> — 除非以书面形式作出并经该方签署",
            "<strong>定语从句：</strong>against whom enforcement of such <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span>, modification, or <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"弃权\">waiver</span> is sought — 被请求执行该修订、修改或弃权的一方",
            "<strong>关键搭配：</strong><span class=\"collocation\">waiver of any provision</span>（对条款的弃权）；<span class=\"collocation\">enforcement is sought</span>（请求执行）"
          ],
          "translation": "对本协议任何条款的修订、修改或弃权，除非以书面形式作出并经被请求执行该修订、修改或弃权的一方签署，否则不具有效力。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "exercises",
      "heading": "4. 练习题",
      "groups": [
        {
          "style": "quiz",
          "title": "练习A：术语匹配",
          "instruction": "选择各术语的正确中文释义。",
          "questions": [
            {
              "prompt": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"前言\">preamble</span>",
              "options": [
                "通用条款",
                "序文",
                "附件",
                "修订"
              ],
              "answer": "序文",
              "explanation": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"前言\">preamble</span> 是合同开头段，载明当事人信息和签约日期。"
            },
            {
              "prompt": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span>",
              "options": [
                "定义条款",
                "实质性条款",
                "鉴于条款",
                "签署"
              ],
              "answer": "鉴于条款",
              "explanation": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span> 是合同序言部分的背景叙述，通常以 <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于\">WHEREAS</span> 开头。"
            },
            {
              "prompt": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款\">boilerplate</span>",
              "options": [
                "附件",
                "通用条款",
                "条款",
                "修正案"
              ],
              "answer": "通用条款",
              "explanation": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款\">boilerplate</span> 指合同尾部的标准化条款，如管辖法律、可分割性、完整协议等。"
            },
            {
              "prompt": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span>（合同语境）",
              "options": [
                "执行死刑",
                "签署",
                "履行",
                "终止"
              ],
              "answer": "签署",
              "explanation": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span> 在合同语境中主要指合同的正式签署，而非日常意义的‘执行’。"
            },
            {
              "prompt": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表\">schedules</span>（合同语境）",
              "options": [
                "时间表",
                "条款",
                "日程",
                "附件"
              ],
              "answer": "附件",
              "explanation": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表\">schedules</span> 是附在合同正文之后的补充文件，包含具体细节、清单或技术参数等。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "style": "quiz",
          "title": "练习B：选词填空",
          "instruction": "根据语境选择最恰当的术语。",
          "questions": [
            {
              "prompt": "The ______ of this Agreement describe the background of the transaction and the parties' intent.",
              "options": [
                "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表\">schedules</span>",
                "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span>",
                "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款\">boilerplate</span>",
                "amendments"
              ],
              "answer": "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span>",
              "explanation": "合同的背景叙述部分称为 <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">recitals</span>。"
            },
            {
              "prompt": "No ______ to this Agreement <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"应当（法律强制义务）\">shall</span> be valid unless executed in writing by both parties.",
              "options": [
                "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定\">provision</span>",
                "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span>",
                "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span>",
                "<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"前言\">preamble</span>"
