      "heading": "6. 今日小结",
      "points": [
        "<strong>合同七段式结构</strong>：<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"合同标题\">Title</span> → <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"前言\">Preamble</span> → <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"鉴于条款\">Recitals</span> → <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"定义条款\">Definitions</span> → <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"实质条款\">Operative Provisions</span> → <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款\">Boilerplate</span> → <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表\">Schedules</span>，这是英文商务合同的标准骨架。",
        "<strong>三个“条款”辨析</strong>：<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条（合同中的大条）\">article</span>（大章节编号）＞ <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"条款\">clause</span>（具体条文）≈ <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"规定\">provision</span>（最通用的正式用语）。",
        "<strong><span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span> 与 <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span></strong>：<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"修正案\">amendment</span> 指对已签合同的修订变更；<span class=\"term\" data-def=\"签署\">execution</span> 在合同语境中特指正式签署，而非日常语义的“执行”。",
        "<strong><span class=\"term\" data-def=\"样板条款\">boilerplate</span> 不等于不重要</strong>：虽是“标准条款”，但管辖法律、争议解决、可分割性等条款直接影响合同的可执行性，实务中须逐条审查。",
        "<strong><span class=\"term\" data-def=\"附表\">schedules</span> 的法律地位</strong>：附件经“incorporated <span class=\"term\" data-def=\"本协议中\">herein</span>”条款纳入后，与合同正文具有同等效力。"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
